<HEAD>State-by-State List of Forbes 400 Richest Americans</HEAD>
<HEAD>With PM-Richest Rich Bjt</HEAD>
<DATELINE>NEW YORK (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Here are the Forbes 400 richest Americans for
1988, grouped by their residences in 39 states, the District of
Columbia and three other nations. Each listing includes a person's
overall ranking, worth in millions, residence, source of wealth and
age.
</TEXT>
